Merge pull request #50 from ingokegel/StyledLabelBuilder_escape

StyledLabelBuilder did not handle unmatched escaped brackets.

commit.message:
StyledLabelBuilder did not handle unmatched escaped brackets.

Formatting in a text like "{text with single \{ fails:f:(128,128,128)}" would not be parsed because findMatchingBracket did not track escapes.
